high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the stove and walk to the counter on the left near the window.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn left, take a left at the stove and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the potato inside the fridge on the bottom shelf, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the island counter ahead.
Put the chilled potato on the counter in front of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato on a counter.

high_descs: turn to the right and move forward to the counter, make a right and move to the center of the counter, turn to the left to face the oval brown object sitting on the counter
pick up the oval brown object from the counter
turn to the left towards the stove and make a left again moving to the fridge on the right side passed the stove, turn to face the fridge
open the fridge door, put the brown oval object in to the fridge on the bottom shelf, close the door for a few seconds, open the door and remove the brown object, close the door
turn around to face the kitchen island
put the brown oval object on to the kitchen island in front of the spatula
anns.task_desc: put a chilled brown oval object on to the kitchen island

high_descs: Turn around and move to the right around the island. Face the counter on the left.
Pick up the potato from the center of the counter.
Carry the potato and move to the left, and face the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and place the potato inside. Shut the door and then open it again. Take out the potato and shut the door.
Carry the potato and turn around to face the island.
Place the potato on the counter, in front of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato and place it on the counter.
